{"data":[{"name":"77:1","price":"Demi (malaikat-malaikat)885) yang diutus untuk membawa kebaikan,","arabic":"وَٱلۡمُرۡسَلَٰتِ عُرۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5623,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"*885) Sebagian mufasir mengartikan “Demi angin yang dikirim.”","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-mur'salāti ʿur'fan ","translations":["By the ones sent forth","one after another","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-mur'salāti","ʿur'fan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1590],[2,1590,2565]]}},{"name":"77:2","price":"dan (malaikat-malaikat) yang terbang dengan kencangnya,886)","arabic":"فَٱلۡعَٰصِفَٰتِ عَصۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5624,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"*886) Terbang untuk melaksanakan perintah Allah.","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-ʿāṣifāti ʿaṣfan ","translations":["And the winds that blow","violently","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-ʿāṣifāti","ʿaṣfan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1640],[2,1640,2905]]}},{"name":"77:3","price":"dan (malaikat-malaikat) yang menyebarkan (rahmat Allah) dengan seluas-luasnya,887)","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِرَٰتِ نَشۡرٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5625,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"*887) Pada waktu malaikat turun untuk membawa wahyu, sebagian mufasir berpendapat bahwa yang dimaksud dengan an-nāsyirāt ialah angin yang bertiup disertai hujan.","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-nāshirāti nashran ","translations":["And the ones that scatter","far and wide","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-nāshirāti","nashran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2130],[2,2130,3365]]}},{"name":"77:4","price":"dan (malaikat-malaikat) yang membedakan (antara yang baik dan yang buruk) dengan sejelas-jelasnya,","arabic":"فَٱلۡفَٰرِقَٰتِ فَرۡقٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5626,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-f